        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Find our Hearts Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Defense to establish a publicly available database&nbsp;containing the names and citations of all members of the U.S. Armed Forces who have been awarded the Purple Heart. </p>]]></text>
